data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. PRICE REDUCTION!!!!!    TURNKEY!!!!!  This Property has what it takes!!!   Location and Value!!!!  Ideally located in the heart of the much sought after, Lakewood Ranch.  This, Select End -Unit offers a private yard surrounded by wooded and natural views of the Florida Landscape.    This one-floor, two-bedroom home features an oversized bath with a double vanity, laundry room with a full-size washer and dryer, attached garage, and a covered porch area.  A spacious kitchen hosts a walk- in pantry, and dining area. Bring your own cosmetic finishes and your pets and enjoy the Lakewood Ranch Lifestyle together!  You will find a remarkable selection of golf courses and restaurants. Shopping at UTC Mall offers over 100 different stores.  Enjoy breathtaking Siesta Key, Lido Key,, Longboat Key, Anna Maria Island at sunrise and sunset.
